Where did they come from?

7
00:01:42,166 --> 00:01:42,750
Hmm.

8
00:02:00,166 --> 00:02:02,291
The Commander is very angry now.

9
00:02:03,875 --> 00:02:05,291
Everyone knows.

10
00:02:06,875 --> 00:02:09,875
If we don't get to the bottom of this,

11
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:12,875
