12
00:02:20,166 --> 00:02:20,833
Don't move.

13
00:02:21,625 --> 00:02:22,208
Stay still.

14
00:02:23,208 --> 00:02:23,791
Put down your gun.

15
00:02:27,750 --> 00:02:28,625
Put down your gun.

16
00:02:44,000 --> 00:02:45,125
My own child.

17
00:02:46,000 --> 00:02:47,416
It's not your place to act out here.

18
00:02:49,500 --> 00:02:50,166
Commander Wang.

19
00:02:51,000 --> 00:02:53,458
As long as the leader isn't corrupt, the ranks won't be either.

20
00:02:54,083 --> 00:02:55,333
Then I have an explanation.

21
00:02:57,125 --> 00:02:58,041
Director Deng, please

22
00:02:58,625 --> 00:03:00,166
rest in the VIP room.

23
00:03:04,250 --> 00:03:04,583
Please.

24
00:03:10,291 --> 00:03:10,625
Let's go.

25
00:03:18,708 --> 00:03:19,500
Everyone here

26
00:03:20,750 --> 00:03:22,750
is a brother who has fought life and death with me.

27
00:03:23,541 --> 00:03:24,250
You all know

28
00:03:25,541 --> 00:03:27,500
the leader and the Party and the Nation have treated us well.

29
00:03:28,083 --> 00:03:28,666
Speak up.

30
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:31,291
What is this all about today?

31
00:03:34,916 --> 00:03:36,208
The Commander personally raised me.

32
00:03:37,250 --> 00:03:38,583
You can execute me today.

33
00:03:40,083 --> 00:03:40,916
The game is up.

34
00:03:41,416 --> 00:03:42,666
This is all out in the open.

35
00:03:43,875 --> 00:03:45,083
If we don't plan ahead,

36
00:03:45,791 --> 00:03:46,750
who will?

37
00:03:49,041 --> 00:03:49,958
Go to Taiwan, China.

38
00:03:50,791 --> 00:03:52,208
What can we do there?

39
00:03:53,666 --> 00:03:54,791
What about our wives and children?

40
00:04:02,500 --> 00:04:03,250
Brothers,

41
00:04:05,083 --> 00:04:08,333
since fighting against the Japanese invaders, we've risked our lives together.

42
00:04:10,666 --> 00:04:12,625
Though I'm your Commander,

43
00:04:12,750 --> 00:04:14,416
I'm also your elder brother.

44
00:04:17,916 --> 00:04:19,166
Today I've made a decision.

45
00:04:20,708 --> 00:04:22,083
The 79th Division will revolt.

46
00:04:23,125 --> 00:04:24,166
We'll join the Communist side.

47
00:04:24,916 --> 00:04:25,541
We'll abandon darkness for light.

48
00:04:35,333 --> 00:04:35,833
Commander.

49
00:04:36,750 --> 00:04:38,250
If we defect to the Communists,

50
00:04:39,291 --> 00:04:40,041
will they even accept us?

51
00:04:41,750 --> 00:04:43,000
We're soldiers of the Kuomintang.

52
00:04:43,541 --> 00:04:44,333
How can we join the Communist side?

53
00:04:47,708 --> 00:04:49,625
I know what everyone's concerns are.

54
00:04:53,083 --> 00:04:55,333
But the Party and the Nation have lost their power, brothers.

55
00:04:56,125 --> 00:04:58,625
I can't drag you all into the fire.

56
00:05:00,041 --> 00:05:01,541
If we don't join the Communists,

57
00:05:01,708 --> 00:05:03,625
we'll all have to go to Taiwan, China.

58
00:05:06,000 --> 00:05:06,916
I know the Party and the Nation's military strength.

59
00:05:09,583 --> 00:05:13,041
The Chief and General Sun Li-jen don't get along.

60
00:05:14,000 --> 00:05:14,833
What about the others?

61
00:05:17,791 --> 00:05:19,291
Useless officials.

62
00:05:23,583 --> 00:05:24,625
If we

63
00:05:25,208 --> 00:05:26,625
really go to Taiwan, China,

64
00:05:28,625 --> 00:05:30,250
I'm afraid in our lifetime

65
00:05:30,416 --> 00:05:34,000
we'll never return.

66
00:05:44,750 --> 00:05:47,083
It's not that I'm ungrateful.

67
00:05:47,083 --> 00:05:48,708
It's the Party and the Nationâ€”

68
00:05:49,958 --> 00:05:52,291
