70
00:06:01,500 --> 00:06:02,166
Those willing to follow me,

71
00:06:03,208 --> 00:06:03,791
take up your weapons.

72
00:06:05,333 --> 00:06:05,833
Those unwilling,

73
00:06:07,083 --> 00:06:07,958
put down your weapons.

74
00:06:08,583 --> 00:06:09,708
or go home and farm,

75
00:06:11,083 --> 00:06:12,250
or join another unit.

76
00:06:13,541 --> 00:06:15,333
If anyone thinks I

77
00:06:15,875 --> 00:06:17,541
don't deserve to live,

78
00:06:18,041 --> 00:06:19,333
you may kill me right here.

79
00:06:19,500 --> 00:06:20,458
I won't object.

80
00:06:27,250 --> 00:06:28,166
If now

81
00:06:30,333 --> 00:06:32,541
someone really shoots me here,

82
00:06:34,583 --> 00:06:35,041
listen up,

83
00:06:36,958 --> 00:06:37,500
don't stop them.

84
00:06:40,166 --> 00:06:40,791
Let him go.

85
00:06:53,791 --> 00:06:54,083
Wait.

86
00:06:54,625 --> 00:06:55,666
Go to the supply office

87
00:06:56,500 --> 00:06:57,083
and draw some travel expenses.

88
00:06:58,208 --> 00:06:59,291
They won't make things difficult for you.

89
00:07:17,625 --> 00:07:18,791
From now on,

90
00:07:20,833 --> 00:07:22,500
we are true brothers.

91
00:07:32,458 --> 00:07:33,333
Go back and get ready now.

92
00:07:34,166 --> 00:07:35,125
We revolt and cross the river tonight.

93
00:07:35,750 --> 00:07:36,333
Yes.

94
00:07:38,000 --> 00:07:39,208
The brothers from our three regiments

95
00:07:39,625 --> 00:07:40,416
