109
00:08:18,041 --> 00:08:20,625
Let's deal with him before we cross the river.

110
00:08:21,625 --> 00:08:23,166
This will be his burial ground.

111
00:08:40,458 --> 00:08:41,583
Commander Wang,

112
00:08:42,666 --> 00:08:43,791
is it the leader that's crooked

113
00:08:44,333 --> 00:08:45,708
or the ranks below?

114
00:08:50,125 --> 00:08:51,083
If the leader isn't crooked,

115
00:08:52,125 --> 00:08:53,625
the ranks won't be crooked either.

116
00:08:55,166 --> 00:08:56,666
You're the one who's crooked.

117
00:08:59,750 --> 00:09:01,250
You want to rebel.
